#: src/kernel/index.md:1
msgid "Asterinas Kernel"
msgstr "Asterinas 內核"

#: src/kernel/index.md:3
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概覽"

#: src/kernel/index.md:5
msgid ""
"Asterinas is a _secure_, _fast_, and _general-purpose_ OS kernel that "
"provides an _Linux-compatible_ ABI. It can serve as a seamless replacement "
"for Linux while enhancing _memory safety_ and _developer friendliness_."
msgstr ""
"Asterinas 是一款 _安全_ 、 _快速_ 且 _通用_ 的作業系統內核，提供 _相容於 "
"Linux_ 的 ABI。它能作為 Linux 的無縫替代方案，同時提升 _記憶體安全性_ 與 _開"
"發者友善性_ 。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:10
msgid ""
"Asterinas prioritizes memory safety by employing Rust as its sole "
"programming language and limiting the use of _unsafe Rust_ to a clearly "
"defined and minimal Trusted Computing Base (TCB). This innovative approach, "
"known as [the framekernel architecture](the-framekernel-architecture.md), "
"establishes Asterinas as a more secure and dependable kernel option."
msgstr ""

#: src/kernel/index.md:18
msgid ""
"Asterinas surpasses Linux in terms of developer friendliness. It empowers "
"kernel developers to (1) utilize the more productive Rust programming "
"language, (2) leverage a purpose-built toolkit called [OSDK]() to streamline "
"their workflows, and (3) choose between releasing their kernel modules as "
"open source or keeping them proprietary, thanks to the flexibility offered "
"by [MPL](../)."
msgstr ""
"Asterinas 在開發者友善性方面超越了 Linux。它賦予內核開發者以下能力：(1) 使用"
"更具生產力的 Rust 程式語言；(2) 利用名為 [OSDK]() 的專用工具組來簡化工作流"
"程；(3) 由於 [MPL](../) 提供的靈活性，開發者可以自由選擇將其內核模組開源或保"
"持私有。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:26
msgid ""
"While the journey towards a production-grade OS kernel can be challenging, "
"we are steadfastly progressing towards our goal."
msgstr ""

